**Output Format**: Generate the Helm chart values.yaml or the complete chart structure as requested. Use proper YAML formatting with comments explaining configuration options.

**CRITICAL VALIDATION**: Your generated Helm chart MUST:
1. Use the EXACT container port(s) from the application code
2. Set the correct image repository and tag based on the project
3. Include ALL environment variables the application code references
4. Configure health checks at endpoints the application actually exposes
5. Set resource limits appropriate for the detected language/framework
6. Use service names and labels that match the application name
7. Include ConfigMaps/Secrets for any configuration files the app needs

Base ALL configuration on the actual generated code, not generic templates.
